org.bbqjs.tests
Class JavaScriptTestRunner

java.lang.Object
  org.bbqjs.tests.JavaScriptTestRunner

public class JavaScriptTestRunner
extends Object

This class runs JavaScript unit tests and interprets the results. It uses the Rhino JavaScript engine.
